reviewText: 有点太简单了哦，只是一些框框架架。这个课程应该有更高的层次，比如说，贵校可以以实例来展现一个课题，估计会有趣并且有用得多。看来，“自由而无用“之精神，还得等我两年后来复旦实践啊！！

The course is a little bit abstract, especially some basic concepts associated the health economics. If the teaching group can introduce more examples when explain some abstract concepts , this course will offer us a much deeper insight in global health.
